Career Paths





Students &Recent Grads
If you want to work on purposeful projects that are helping make the world a safer place, make Raytheon your choice. Alongside an array of fulltime opportunities, we offer robust internships, co-ops and Leadership Development Program roles – all of which offer the training, development and experiences you need to stand out and change the world. Read More


Production & Maintenance
Delivering quality and superior manufacturability in all of our product areas is thanks in no small part to our Production and Maintenance team. As part of their operations, you too will be integral to upholding the reputation of our technology – and making the world a safer place in the process. Read More


Professional
A global enterprise of our size and scope offers more opportunities than you could probably ever imagine. Whatever your area of expertise and experience, there’s an excellent chance we have a professional career waiting for you – one that allows you to develop your talents as you make the world a safer place.  Read More


Veterans
As a leading supplier of technologies to the U.S. military and our allies, we place enormous value on the strategic and tactical talents that only veterans can offer. Working with us provides an opportunity to bring your battlefield skills to the private sector, and continue making the world a safer place.   Read More







